                        <div class="face front">
                            <h3 id="module-title-connect">свържи</h3>
                            <img src="~/Content/images/modules-connect.png" alt="Module Connect">
                        </div>
                        <div class="face back">
                            <p>Offal neutra helvetica, sustainable beard next level plaid. Gastropub four loko health goth, chicharrones etsy kale chips sustainable. Pork belly fanny pack readymade intelligentsia XOXO.</p>
